ame":"마리나","body":"저기, 촬영은 어떤 느낌이었어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev77-me4-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"촬영은 긴장감도 있었는데요……\n그래도 편안하고 무척 즐거웠어요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev77-me4-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"밖에서의 촬영이 많았기에\n모두한테 배식이 나왔거든요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev77-me4-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"마리나","body":"촬영 중의 배식이라……\n이야기는 들었는데 진짜 그런 게 있구나.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev77-me4-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"커다란 냄비로 카레나 장국을 만들어 주셔서……\n무척 맛있었어요!","tention"